{"h7e1d6ad7gd641g4863gaa20g62d2f93d61db": ["I have a travelling companion. I hardly need another.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "hfbd90b7cg4af1g4121g8feagc8ed8c61159b": ["I'm not interested in talking to you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "h00da4993gaeb1g482cgbce9g43347b416b5d": ["Do you mind? I'm <i>very </i>busy.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "hd0012838g8fd8g4c5cg8f8egfb5fe9e89b73": ["Sorry, but I'm spoken for.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "h169ac011g1345g413bga592g3f6492c413f7": ["Do excuse me, please. Frightfully busy.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "h1d91ae1eg29d9g4ee2gb333ge4342ed638b8": ["Whatever it is, I'm afraid I can't help you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "h52045293g3f19g46d9ga42ag5f0c740bc435": ["| Sorry, I'm with someone else right now. |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "h0e4247eeg18f6g40e2g809fga232abbcf7e6": ["| Sorry, I'm with someone else right now. |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "ha3ade107gbe07g4047gbe5bgc20bf13b5b4f": ["I have allied with another.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "hb95b300fg0c95g4c10g9623g31ed379b8947": ["I've no business with you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "ha2b1499age533g4014gb851g4ec3050d00ec": ["<i>Chk. </i>I've no need for friends.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "hfd61a6ccg4914g4d6dg8dd4geb5c2db7eb33": ["| Sorry, I'm with someone else right now. |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "he298665fgc438g429bg86f4g14a3bad2e6ce": ["There's nothing for you and I to discuss. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "h37a6bb0cgd46ag4565g9f4dg4181c7b9ca4d": ["You'll have to confide in someone else. I'm spoken for.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "h984b1965g457cg48c9g9ab9g413ad4e0eb02": ["You'll have to look elsewhere for company - I already have an arrangement. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "h12d8e22ag93a8g4cd9ga822gc224fd88c90b": ["There's little I can say to you, I'm afraid. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "hcd40eef3g9669g4bdcgb266g217089c53c8b": ["Sorry - there's only so much of the Blade to go around.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "h1fd57197ge8adg47c3gb312g897294fb7c3e": ["You've got gusto, but I'm bound to another.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"], "h7f90ea7ag9963g4166ga12eg5caec91b01a0": ["You seem nice and all, but I've teamed up with someone else.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Global\\GLO_AD_NonBondedCompanionDialog.html", "3a106b26-8953-7c7d-ba2b-6e998377b218"]}